{"tid":2215770,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［警世文］今時今日嘅打工仔想係職場升職，無家底人脈已經輸九成","createTime":"2020-09-24T08:04:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T01:57:23.000Z","uid":376073,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ecc0dd92e15e7bb5819ddeadfc300a3b2e9148bc","tid":2215770,"uid":376073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:04:33.000Z","msg":"唔好講你叻到識飛，間公司無咗你就執笠。<br />\n事實係普通打工仔做嘅工作內容隨時都有人可以頂上，所以對公司，對老細來講，你班打工仔只係賤民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n職場上只有2種人可以做贏家：<br />\n1）你有人脈，只要你老豆老母阿叔姑姐係對你老細有幫助嘅人，有利益關係嘅人，你日日準時收工都照升，咩好嘢學到嘢嘅project都係比晒你。<br />\n2) 有家底，打份風流工，只要你有錢過你老細，你老細無咩事都唔會得罪你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後我想重申：<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">公屋仔ot到12點 = 正常office hour<br />\n太子爺皇親國戚ot 5分鐘 = 上進升職 </span>"},{"pid":"dd5d61bb81868eeb1b10d47c97d3fc2a2466ff1d","tid":2215770,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:09:42.000Z","msg":"所以唔識人嘅都係做公墓員掛鈎嘅公營機構好<br />\n起碼你唔升職都有point跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f6fe963e2931f057ef0dc04cb1aa979ffcdd4d0","tid":2215770,"uid":376073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd5d61bb81868eeb1b10d47c97d3fc2a2466ff1d","tid":2215770,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:09:42.000Z","msg":"所以唔識人嘅都係做公墓員掛鈎嘅公營機構好<br />\n起碼你唔升職都有point跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:21:45.000Z","msg":"無錯，咪慢慢hea到max point 日日準時收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1bc585f34a07917ed74d7058afce464dd377fea","tid":2215770,"uid":376073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:08:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5ef50f7f0070c5bccc1bae2d729799ef41e0ea0","tid":2215770,"uid":376073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1bc585f34a07917ed74d7058afce464dd377fea","tid":2